<title>USA: REX Stores plans buyback up to 500,000 shrs.</title>
<headline>REX Stores plans buyback up to 500,000 shrs.</headline>
<dateline>DAYTON, Ohio 1997-02-03</dateline>
<text>
<p>REX Stores Corp said on Monday it authorized the purchase of up to an additional 500,000 shares of its common stock in addition to previous authorizations.</p>
<p>The company said the purchases will be made in the market or private transactions at prevailing market prices.</p>
<p>REX said it has 8,213,731 shares outstanding of common stock as of Jan 31. It purchased 629,600 shares of its common stock during the fourth quarter and bought a total of 854,000 shares during fiscal year 1997 as part of its existing authorization to acquire up to one million shares.</p>
